        {
            "title": "高官樓王｜胡健民2368萬買大埔比華利山別墅 坐擁逾14項物業",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"634\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RAk6gudGV8UIrBFqrt_y2g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/0db7a5a7d3580e051da616dd05d9c4f7\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">擁有14項物業、被指為高官「樓王」的現任政制及內地事務局副局長<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"胡健民\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:胡健民;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/胡健民\">胡健民</a>再度入市買樓，新近以2,368萬元買入大埔<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"比華利山別墅\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:比華利山別墅;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/比華利山別墅\">比華利山別墅</a>一個逾2,000方呎的五房巨宅，料購入作為投資收租之用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">資料顯示，大埔比華利山別墅銀池道單號屋，實用面積2,079方呎，5房間隔，另連930方呎花園及513方呎天台，以2,368萬成交，呎價11,390元。原業主2012年以約3,236.5萬元買入，持貨14年，帳面蝕868.5萬元或27％。新買家為海敏有限公司，公司股東包括胡健民及其妻子黃美玉等相關人士。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e707ea4a-826b-360b-b8db-f367de1a8beb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據港府資料，胡健民提交的利益申報，他持有14個物業，包括3個在香港，10個在廣東，1個在馬來西亞，另外在加拿大擁有兩幅土地。翻查資料，上述海敏有限公司於2010年及2011年先後購入大埔淺月灣2間洋房，分別作價1,593萬元及2,415萬元，其中一間為自住物業。上周，他加入一項利益申報，以海敏全資持有一個大埔連車位的住宅單位作出租，估計正是上述大埔比華利山別墅成交單位。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":0,\"yLinkElement\":\"img\"}' data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://lgltdclass.com/ken_freeclassreg_bmyt/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CFOCMTzEz4og89TU7pLaow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzMw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/ae6af5ac577c6b197341c289fcb33169\" width=\"900\"/></div></a></div>",
