        {
            "title": "彭博:軟銀尋求以OpenAI股份作抵押取得100億美元保證金貸款",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3_c1iWTDssdyXdYkg9X8Ag--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED4A07F_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 據彭博新聞週三援引知情人士報導,軟銀集團(TYO:9984)正尋求以其持有的美國<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"人工智能\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:人工智能;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人工智能\">人工智能</a>公司OpenAI股份作抵押,取得100億美元貸款。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這筆擬議的保證金貸款將以該公司持有的OpenAI股份作為抵押品,凸顯出這家日本企業集團為了資助人工智能板塊投資而承擔額外債務,深化其在人工智能領域的佈局。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">東京上市的軟銀股價週四上漲6%,與大盤走勢一致。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報導,該貸款期限為兩年,並可選擇延長一年,但討論仍在進行中,條款可能會有所變動。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e9c02a2c-8ced-388b-8c22-f4d174fefd01-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此舉正值軟銀在創辦人孫正義領導下加速推進其人工智能戰略之際,該公司已透過旗下願景基金向OpenAI投入數百億美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上個月,該公司獲得了400億美元過渡性貸款,以支持其對ChatGPT開發商日益增長的投資以及一般企業用途,凸顯出其越來越依賴槓桿來資助其人工智能雄心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A-%E8%BB%9F%E9%8A%80%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E4%BB%A5openai%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD%E4%BD%9C%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%BC%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97100%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89%E9%87%91%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE-025655743.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 11:14:40",
