        {
            "title": "伊朗談判陷僵局、荷莫茲海峽持續受阻,布蘭特原油突破102美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t8H8YwWPBRcVaBSDkEjFBg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_1_M_1440048330.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週四亞洲交易時段,油價進一步上漲,美國與伊朗之間鮮有新談判跡象,而<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荷莫茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:荷莫茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/荷莫茲海峽\">荷莫茲海峽</a>在本週發生船隻襲擊事件後,航運活動仍然稀少。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價在本週稍早經歷劇烈波動,但在美國總統川普宣布無限期延長與伊朗的停火協議後,週三收高。不過,華盛頓和德黑蘭退出了在巴基斯坦舉行的潛在和平談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間21:24(格林威治標準時間01:24),布蘭特原油期貨上漲0.4%至102.33美元/桶,美國WTI原油期貨上漲0.6%至93.52美元/桶。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c13bdadc-ec8e-3d06-b6d9-7436066455fa-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週三油價大幅上漲,此前伊朗在荷莫茲海峽攻擊並扣押兩艘船隻,導致該水道基本關閉。美國對該國維持海軍封鎖,引發德黑蘭不滿。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">即使在川普無限期延長停火協議後,美伊和平談判的狀況仍完全不明朗。本週報導顯示,華盛頓還在更廣泛的亞洲水域追蹤伊朗船隻。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗已排除在美國維持海軍封鎖期間進行任何停火談判的可能性。川普則呼籲德黑蘭在簽署任何重大和平協議之前完全重新開放荷莫茲海峽,使兩國陷入僵局。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荷莫茲海峽已成為伊朗衝突的關鍵焦點,其關閉阻斷了全球約20%的石油供應。預計亞洲和中東經濟體將受到供應中斷的最嚴重打擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E9%99%B7%E5%83%B5%E5%B1%80-%E8%8D%B7%E8%8E%AB%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB-%E5%B8%83%E8%98%AD%E7%89%B9%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4102%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-024146216.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 11:14:43",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "簡訊：國藥盈收雖齊升 首季現金流出續擴大",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Dipxa1AXqkZK6y7jgD1tBA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/the_bamboo_works_186/4aabaea11fae4ec296b82206939a8c91\" width=\"500\"/></div></figure></div>",
